name: Multi-dimensional-GPU-Indexing
tagline: This is the project for indexing multi-dimensional datasets
body:
### About this project
Numerous sensors and simulators generate a large amount of data every day. Big data processing is no longer a choice but an inescapable situation. 

Multi-dimensional indexing is the one of the most common access patterns in scientific applications such as a geometric map application, image processing, etc.

GPU has successfully accelerated the performance ... 

### Authors and Contributors
